title: Jodorowsky & Moebius - The [Original] Incal vol 5-6 - fix
description:
Okay, second time's the charm, sorry about that.

Here's hoping ill88eagle sees this...

Anyway, this is book 5 & 6 of the Incal, created by Jodorowsky and Moebius, translated by Epic/Marvel comics back in the eighties. 

Book 1-4 can be found here: http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/4900818/Jodorowsky__amp__Moebius_-_The_%5BOriginal%5D_Incal_vol_1-4_%5BCBR%5D

Take this as another pretty please for a translation of no. 7 ill88eagle. 

For some reason I can't seem to comment on torrents, but I hope you'll do the remaining three albums of Bilal's Hatzfeld tetralogy too, I see you're uploading some of his stuff now! Oh, and the last part of the metabarons, and maybe the first one, without the missing pages of the DC/Humanoids english edition. ;) I'm looking forward to it!
